  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2933",
  "title": "clearAllURL should be a function in connectCurrentRefinedValues",
  "body": "clearAllURL is documented as a function but is actually a string. We will fix that in the doc so that we are consistent and do not break the current implementations (next minor). But for consistency with createUrl, it should be a function (next major).\r\n\r\nMaybe we should update the name in this case, or think about changing the signature of the createURL function:\r\n - `createURL() => url with everything cleared`\r\n - `createURL(facet) => url with just facet cleared`",
